dium. Our novel approach\noffers the tools needed to quantify the effects of outflows on galactic\nmagnetic fields as well as their influence on the intergalactic medium and\nevolution of energetic particles.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 5 Feb 2021 19:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 15 Apr 2021 15:51:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-23"}
