 EFT approach, and are\nconsistent with GR singularity theorems, yet are general and extend them, as\nthe singularity theorems indicate breakdown at a strong field limit of GR in\nblack holes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 6 Feb 2021 08:35:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 22 Jan 2022 01:46:19 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 4 Jun 2022 01:50:21 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 20 Dec 2022 22:11:01 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Sat, 25 Mar 2023 14:24:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-28"}
