ea. These\nfindings suggest the possibility of a practical EEG-based treatment strategy\nthat can accurately predict FOG episodes, excluding the potential confound of\nvoluntary stopping.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 6 Feb 2021 12:04:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-09"}
